    <h1>Messaging Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <h2>Program Description</h2>
    <p>Land Lotus, operated by Quill Adventures LLC ("Land Lotus," "we," "us"), offers an SMS messaging program for landowners interested in selling vacant or rural land. If you opt in, we send text messages about your property, including cash-offer details, follow-up questions, appointment scheduling, and coordination of closing paperwork.</p>

    <h2>How to Opt In</h2>
    <p>Participation is entirely voluntary. You may opt in by checking the SMS consent box on our <a href="contact.html">contact form</a>, or by texting us first at 702-819-0031. <strong>Providing your consent to receive text messages is optional and is not a condition of submitting our form, receiving an offer, or completing any purchase or transaction with us.</strong></p>

    <h2>Message Frequency</h2>
    <p>Message frequency varies based on your conversation with us and the stage of any potential transaction.</p>

    <h2>Cost</h2>
    <p>Message and data rates may apply, depending on your mobile carrier and plan. Land Lotus does not charge for the messages themselves.</p>

    <h2>How to Opt Out</h2>
    <p>You can cancel the SMS program at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message. After you send STOP, we will send one confirmation message and then stop sending SMS messages. Opt-out requests are honored immediately and permanently.</p>

    <h2>Help</h2>
    <p>Reply <strong>HELP</strong> to any message for assistance, or contact us at hello@landlotus.com or 702-840-5350.</p>

    <h2>Supported Carriers &amp; Delivery</h2>
    <p>Carriers are not liable for delayed or undelivered messages. Message delivery is subject to the effective transmission from your wireless service provider and is outside our control.</p>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>We do not share or sell mobile opt-in data or SMS consent information with any third parties or affiliates for marketing purposes. Your consent to receive text messages is never shared with anyone for their own marketing. For full details on how we handle your information, see our <a href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Quill Adventures LLC (Land Lotus)<br />Phone: 702-840-5350<br />Email: hello@landlotus.com<br />Website: landlotus.com</p>
